This directory contains some python routines for plotting simulac
output for the lambda phage example.

To generate the simulations, run the following commands

  $ mkdir test			# create directory for data files
  $ cp lambda.cfg test		# copy configuration file to data dir
  $ python gensims.py -s test	# run simulation batch

To plot the results of the simulations, use the following commands:

  $ ipython -pylab
  In [1]: from arkin import *	# Import plotting functions
  In [2]: fig3()		# Generate plot; when prompted, select the
				# 'test' directory


